{"arkId":"cl010095025","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010095025","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Adonis","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Adonis"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1602","currentLocation":"Denon, [SCULPT] Salle 403 - Galerie Michel-Ange","room":"Salle 403, Aile Aile Denon, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":"","endYear":1602,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Prestinari, Marcantonio","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Italie","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 3678","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statue","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Inscription sur la plinthe\u00a0: \u00ab\u00a0ADONIS PENE REDIVIVUS \/ PYRRHI VICECOMITIS BORROMAEI LARGITATE\u00a0\u00bb (Adonis presque rendu \u00e0 la vie par la g\u00e9n\u00e9rosit\u00e9 de Piero\u00a0Visconti-Borromeo)\r ; Sur le baudrier\u00a0au revers\u00a0: \u00ab\u00a0MARCI ANTONII PRISTINARI MEDIOLANEN [SIS] MANU\u00a0\u00bb (de la main de Marco Antonio Prestinari, milanais)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,6","displayDimension":"2,6 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,8","displayDimension":"0,8 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,7","displayDimension":"0,7 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre de Candoglia (?)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"Milan (Italie) (Villa Lainate)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Command\u00e9 par le comte Pirro Visconti-Borromeo (vers 1530-1604), pour le d\u00e9cor de sa villa situ\u00e9e \u00e0 Lainate, dans les environs de Milan. Ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 vers 1600-1602 et mentionn\u00e9 dans un \u00e9tat des dettes et cr\u00e9ances du d\u00e9funt, mort en 1604, \u00e9tabli pour ses h\u00e9ritiers, pour la p\u00e9riode 1602-1604. Prestinari y figure pour deux paiements \u00ab\u00a0per una statua di marmo di Addone come dil mandato\u00a0\u00bb pour la villa Visconti-Borromei. Une description ancienne (cit\u00e9e par Luca\u00a0Beltrami) mentionne la statue d\u2019Adonis dans les jardins de la villa Lainate, devenue villa Litta \u00e0 partir de 1678, puis villa Weill-Weiss \u00e0 la fin du XIXe si\u00e8cle. Acquis vers 1935 par l\u2019antiquaire milanais Giovani Balzani. Ancienne collection Ephrussi, puis famille de Broglie au ch\u00e2teau de Vaux-le-P\u00e9nil (Seine-et-Marne). Commerce d\u2019art, Paris. Acquis en 1984 (comit\u00e9s du 21 juin et 4 octobre, conseil du 10\u00a0octobre, arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 18 octobre 1984).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Giovanni BALZANI","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art"},{"value":"Pirro Visconti Borromeo","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"21\/06\/1984","startYear":1984,"endYear":1984},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"04\/10\/1984","startYear":1984,"endYear":1984},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"10\/10\/1984","startYear":1984,"endYear":1984},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00e